<L>__{exterior camp main gate night}
<A>__{the guard in the sentry box glances up from a newspaper at the sound of an approaching motorbike. a young woman wearing an ao dai and coolie hat rides up on a honda scooter and stops by the shack. over the girl's shoulder as she steps up to the guards box and coos something to the sentry. he grins to see a new face among the whores from the village, and one so pretty... great luck.}
<B>__{reverse on girl}
<A>__{revealing that she is co, as she dickers price through the sentry box window. he unlatches the gate.}
